<subSubSection pageNumber="315" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="315">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="315">Note:</emphasis>
Nardi (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="315">Taxon</emphasis>
37: 978. 1988) proposed the rejection of the name and the Committee for Spermatophyta eventually (
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="315">l.c.</emphasis>
54: 1093. 2005) recommended this, confirmed by the General Committee (
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="315">l.c.</emphasis>
55: 800. 2006). As a result, the correct name for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Aristolochiaceae" genus="Aristolochia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Piperales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="315">A. longa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
becomes 
<taxonomicName authority="Boiss. &amp; Reut." authorityName="Boiss. &amp; Reut." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Aristolochiaceae" genus="Aristolochia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Piperales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fontanesii">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="315">A. fontanesii</emphasis>
Boiss. &amp; Reut.
</taxonomicName>
; see De Groot &amp; al. (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="315">Bot. J. Linn. Soc.</emphasis>
151: 223. 2006).
</paragraph>
